msgstr "取得最新原始碼"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../developers.rst:56
msgid ""
"Before we can fix any bugs or add any features, we need to get the source "
"code onto your computer."
msgstr "在修復錯誤或新增功能之前，我們需要將原始碼下載到您的電腦。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../developers.rst:59
msgid "Use git to clone our 3 repositories:"
